# Jewelry Store Ecommerce Database

This project contains a MySQL relational database for an ecommerce jewelry website.

## Database Tables

Customers – stores customer information  
Products – jewelry items available for purchase  
Orders – customer purchase records  
Shipping – shipping information for orders  
Authentication – login credentials for customers  

## Sample Data

The database includes:

- 5 customers
- 5 products
- Orders connected to customers and products
- Shipping records
- Authentication accounts for each customer

## How to Run

Import the SQL file into MySQL.

Example:

CREATE DATABASE jewelry_store;
USE jewelry_store;
SOURCE ecommerce_database.sql;
